name: Relatedconditions_hypertensionI10
title: relatedconditions_hypertension I10
description: I20.8 and I24.8 and possibly I25.89 become non-billable 2024.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Conditions other than essential hypertension that are closely related to essential hypertension.),(Data Element Scope: Codes that may be in FHIR resources associated with Problem List and Past Medical History (Condition resource)),(Inclusion Criteria: Conditions related to essential hypertension, including: * Secondary hypertension * Hypertension associated with pregnancy * Atherosclerosis * Cerebrovascular disease/TIA/Stroke * Hypertensive heart disease/heart failure * Chronic kidney disease * Ischemic heart disease),(Exclusion Criteria: Variations of those conditions related to pulmonary hypertension, fetal disorders, and complications of abortion)
